@{
    ViewBag.Title = "SIR";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Products.cshtml";
}
<div>
    <h1>FAQ </h1>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            WHAT IS ATA Store?
        </div>
        <div class="faq-Answer">
            The ATA Store is your source for coding materials, study resources, forms, stationery, patient education material, displays and so much more. 
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            HOW DO I CONTACT CUSTOMER SUPPORT?
        </div>
        <div class="faq-Answer">
            For immediate assistance during business hours, please call 800-282-5463. You can also send email correspondence to 
            <a href="mailto:orders@trucking.org">orders@trucking.org</a>. 
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            WHAT ARE MY PAYMENT OPTIONS?
        </div>
         <div class="faq-Answer">
            All ATA Store orders must be paid at time of purchase. VISA, MasterCard, and American Express are all accepted. For check orders, please verify shipping and applicable tax before mailing payment.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            HOW DO I LOG IN TO THE ATA Store?
        </div>
         <div class="faq-Answer">
            You can access the ATA Store directly by visiting <a href="@System.Configuration.ConfigurationManager.AppSettings["ApplicationUrl"].ToString()" target="_blank">@System.Configuration.ConfigurationManager.AppSettings["ApplicationUrl"].ToString()</a>.  For information on how to log in, visit our <a href="../Login/Index" target="_blank">login assistance</a> page.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            HOW DO I RECEIVE MY MEMBER DISCOUNT?  
        </div>
        <div class="faq-Answer">
            Members must log in under their Member account to take advantage of member discounts. If you are uncertain of your member status,
            please call  800-282-5463. You can also learn more about joining the ATA Store by visiting our 
            <a href="http://www.trucking.org/Join.aspx" target="_blank">Join Now</a> page on our website.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            ARE QUANTITY DISCOUNTS AVAILABLE?  
        </div>
        <div class="faq-Answer">
            There are quantity discounts available for many of the ATA Store products. If you require a quantity not available on the Marketplace,
            please call 800-282-5463 for assistance.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            I AM LOCATED OUTSIDE THE U.S. HOW DO I ORDER ATA Store PRODUCTS?  
        </div>
        <div class="faq-Answer">
            Please call us at 800-282-5463 for assistance. 
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            DOES THE ATA Store SHIP TO P.O. BOXES?  
        </div>
         <div class="faq-Answer">
            Standard orders are shipped via UPS, which requires a street address. If you would prefer to receive your order at a PO Box address, 
             please let us know by calling 800-282-5463 at the time of ordering. 
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            DO YOU OFFER EXPRESS SHIPPING?  
        </div>
        <div class="faq-Answer">
            Yes, in most cases. Please call us at 800-282-5463 for additional information on expedited orders and UPS Next Day service.  Some products are not available for express delivery, so please call before ordering.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            HOW DO I ORDER CUSTOMIZED/PERSONALIZED PRODUCTS?  
        </div>
         <div class="faq-Answer">
            <p>Select the customizable product you are interested in ordering. Then click on the "Custom" box. This will display the pricing for this product. Now click on the "add to cart" button. At this point, if you are not already logged on to the ATA Store, you will be asked to log in. If you have an existing account, you would use your standard login information. However, if you are not an member and have also never previously ordered product through the ATA Store, you would then need to register.</p>
            <p>
            </p>
            Once you are successfully logged in, you will then be directed to a page which provides all the text fields available for customization. Fill out the fields which correspond with your personalization needs and then click the "create proof" button. Once you do so, your proof will be automatically generated and presented to you for review. To inspect the proof up close, click the "View Sample PDF" link just below the product image and wait ten to twenty seconds for the proof PDF to load. If you wish to then add this product to your order, simply click the "add to order" button and proceed with your order. Please note that all customized product sales are final. You are responsible for reviewing your customized content.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="question-container">
            WHAT SHOULD I DO IF I CANNOT FIND A PRODUCT ONLINE?  
        </div>
        <div class="faq-Answer">
            Due to certain limitations, not all ATA Store products are available online. To inquire about a particular product, please call the ATA Store at
            800-282-5463.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
